    "causal_summary": "The live context-server RSS dropped sharply after the embedder cleanup packets, but `memory_health` still cannot attribute RSS to V8 heap, external memory, ArrayBuffers, or retained caches. Without byte-aware telemetry, future memory packets can mistake SQLite/native/external residency for JavaScript heap retention.",
